ivardefs.name: administeredBy
ivardefs.desc: An organization which administer other services such as underwriting, customer service and/or claims processing on behalf of the health insurance product owner.

ivardefs.name: alias_
ivardefs.desc: A list of alternate names that the product is known as, or was known as in the past.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: The contact for the health insurance product for a certain purpose.

ivardefs.name: coverageArea_
ivardefs.desc: The geographic region in which a health insurance product's benefits apply.

ivardefs.name: coverage_
ivardefs.desc: Details about the coverage offered by the insurance product.

ivardefs.name: endpoint_
ivardefs.desc: The technical endpoints providing access to services operated for the health insurance product.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business identifiers assigned to this health insurance product which remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: Official name of the health insurance product as designated by the owner.

ivardefs.name: network_
ivardefs.desc: Reference to the network included in the health insurance product.

ivardefs.name: ownedBy
ivardefs.desc: The entity that is providing  the health insurance product and underwriting the risk.  This is typically an insurance carriers, other third-party payers, or health plan sponsors comonly referred to as 'payers'.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period of time that the health insurance product is available.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The current state of the health insurance product.

ivardefs.name: type_
ivardefs.desc: The kind of health insurance product.

properties.desc: Details of a Health Insurance product/plan provided by an organization.
